						<h2>专利法规</h2>
						<div class="col-md-4 bottom-grids-left-left">
							<img class="img-responsive name-in" src="http://www.inewgrowing.com/uploadfile/2015/1012/20151012023542598.png" title="name" />
						</div>
						<div class="col-md-8 bottom-grids-left-right">
							<p style="box-sizing: border-box !important; padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px; min-height: 1em; padding-left: 0px; width: 563px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; font: 16px/1.75em 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; white-space: pre-wrap; height: 26px; color: rgb(62,62,62); clear: both; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box !important; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; padding-top: 0px">一、UPOV 成立的时间和背景</strong><br />
&nbsp;</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box !important; padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px; min-height: 1em; padding-left: 0px; width: 607px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; font: 16px/1.75em 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; white-space: pre-wrap; height: 311px; color: rgb(62,62,62); clear: both; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">植物新品种保护又称植物育种者权利保护，是对植物新品种的知识产权保护形式，它与专利权、著作权、商标专用权一样，同属于知识产权范畴。目前，世界上许多国家都制定了保护植物新品种的相关法规，采用专利法、专门法或行政法规等方式对植物新品种进行有效保护。其中，比较成熟的保护制度主要是欧洲等<span style="box-sizing: border-box !important; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; background: yellow; padding-top: 0px">植物育种发达国家力推的ＵＰＯＶ模式</span>，即《国际植物新品种保护公约》（以下简称ＵＰＯＶ公约）。<span style="box-sizing: border-box !important; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; background: yellow; padding-top: 0px">ＵＰＯＶ公约于１９６８年生效，对植物新品种保护的起点、保护时期、保护的范围等方面作出规定。</span>ＵＰＯＶ公约分别于<span style="box-sizing: border-box !important; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; background: yellow; padding-top: 0px">１９７２</span>年、<span style="box-sizing: border-box !important; padding-bottom: 0px; background-color: yellow; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; padding-top: 0px">１９７８</span>年和<span style="box-sizing: border-box !important; padding-bottom: 0px; background-color: yellow; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; padding-top: 0px">１９９１</span>年在日内瓦经过三次修改，逐渐成为世界上最主要的植物新品种保护制度，目前生效的有１９７８年与１９９１年的两个文本，ＵＰＯＶ公约１９７８年文本是在１９６１年公约的基础上，经１９７２年１１月和１９７８年１０月两次在日内瓦修订后的文本。<span style="box-sizing: border-box !important; padding-bottom: 0px; background-color: yellow; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; padding-top: 0px">公约１９７８年文本在瑞士、南非、新西兰、爱尔兰、美国、丹麦等国家加入后于１９８１年１１月８日正式生效。</span></p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box !important; padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px; min-height: 1em; padding-left: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; font: 16px/1.75em 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62,62,62); clear: both; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px"><br />
１９９１年３月在瑞士日内瓦召开的植物新品种保护会议上，成员国一致通过了ＵＰＯＶ公约１９９１年文本。该公约规定只有等到有５个成员国批准后才能生效，１９９８年４月２４日ＵＰＯＶ公约１９９１年文本正式生效。目前，加入ＵＰＯＶ公约１９９１年文本已逐渐成为发展潮流。<span style="box-sizing: border-box !important; padding-bottom: 0px; background-color: yellow; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; padding-top: 0px">我国于１９９９年４月２３日加入</span>《国际植物新品种保护公约》<span style="box-sizing: border-box !important; padding-bottom: 0px; background-color: yellow; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; padding-top: 0px">１９７８年文本</span>，成为ＵＰＯＶ的<span style="box-sizing: border-box !important; padding-bottom: 0px; background-color: yellow; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; padding-top: 0px">第３９个成员国</span>，新品种的保护工作得到较快地发展。</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box !important; padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px; min-height: 1em; padding-left: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; font: 16px/26px 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62,62,62); clear: both; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box !important; padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px; min-height: 1em; padding-left: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; font: 16px/1.75em 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62,62,62); clear: both; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box !important; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; padding-top: 0px">二、ＵＰＯＶ公约１９９１年文本与１９７８年文本的区别</strong></p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box !important; padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px; min-height: 1em; padding-left: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; font: 16px/1.75em 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62,62,62); clear: both; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box !important; padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px; min-height: 1em; padding-left: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; font: 16px/1.75em 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62,62,62); clear: both; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">每一次的修正都是为了更好地适应社会的发展，１９９１年文本正是为了适应科技和经济发展而对原公约文本进行适当调整和改进的结果，实施ＵＰＯＶ公约１９９１年文本，将对育种者权益或者植物新品种进行更加有效的保护，它与１９７８年文本主要区别如下：</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box !important; padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px; min-height: 1em; padding-left: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; font: 16px/26px 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62,62,62); clear: both; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box !important; padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px; min-height: 1em; padding-left: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; font: 16px/1.75em 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62,62,62); clear: both; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box !important; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; padding-top: 0px"><span style="box-sizing: border-box !important; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; background: yellow; padding-top: 0px">１．品种权保护形式不同</span></strong></p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box !important; padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px; min-height: 1em; padding-left: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; font: 16px/1.75em 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62,62,62); clear: both; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box !important; padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px; min-height: 1em; padding-left: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; font: 16px/1.75em 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62,62,62); clear: both; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">从保护形式上看，１９７８年文本允许成员国利用专门法和专利法，或者选择其一来保护，但对于同一植物的同一品种不能同时用两种形式双重保护。１９９１年文本修改了这一规定，<span style="box-sizing: border-box !important; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; background: yellow; padding-top: 0px">允许对同一植物品种实行双轨制保护。</span></p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box !important; padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px; min-height: 1em; padding-left: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; font: 16px/1.75em 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62,62,62); clear: both; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box !important; padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px; min-height: 1em; padding-left: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; font: 16px/1.75em 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62,62,62); clear: both; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box !important; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; padding-top: 0px"><span style="box-sizing: border-box !important; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; background: yellow; padding-top: 0px">２．品种权保护的范围不同</span></strong></p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box !important; padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px; min-height: 1em; padding-left: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; font: 16px/1.75em 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62,62,62); clear: both; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box !important; padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px; min-height: 1em; padding-left: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; font: 16px/1.75em 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62,62,62); clear: both; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">１９７８年文本对保护植物属和种的数量要求比较低，对具有约束力的硬性规定，如实施保护的属或种的数量和逐步扩大保护范围的期限，比较宽容和弹性。该文本规定：每个联盟成员国自本公约在其领土生效之日起，应至少对５个属或种实施本公约的规定。随后，每个联盟成员国于本公约在其领土生效之日起的以下期限内，应对更多的属或种实施本公约的规定：（１）３年内至少有ｌ０个属或种；</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box !important; padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px; min-height: 1em; padding-left: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; font: 16px/1.75em 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62,62,62); clear: both; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">（２）６年内至少有１８个属种；</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box !important; padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px; min-height: 1em; padding-left: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; font: 16px/1.75em 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62,62,62); clear: both; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">（３）８年内至少有２４个属或种。</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box !important; padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px; min-height: 1em; padding-left: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; font: 16px/1.75em 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62,62,62); clear: both; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">在申请国及成员国提出特殊困难情况下，可以对上述保护属、种数量限额裁减以及期限延长的规定。修订后的１９９１文本则要求：<span style="box-sizing: border-box !important; padding-bottom: 0px; background-color: yellow; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; padding-top: 0px">最迟自上述（受本公约约束）之日起，至５年期满时，适用于所有植物属和种。对联盟的新成员国则要求：自受本公约约束之日起，至少适用于１５个植物属和种；最迟自上述之日起，至１０年期满时，适用于所有植物属和种。１９９１年文本明显对扩大植物品种保护范围、加快全部植物品种保护进度提出更高、更硬性的要求</span>。</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box !important; padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px; min-height: 1em; padding-left: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; font: 16px/26px 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62,62,62); clear: both; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box !important; padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px; min-height: 1em; padding-left: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; font: 16px/1.75em 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62,62,62); clear: both; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box !important; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; padding-top: 0px"><span style="box-sizing: border-box !important; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; background: yellow; padding-top: 0px">３．品种权保护力度不同</span></strong></p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box !important; padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px; min-height: 1em; padding-left: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; font: 16px/1.75em 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62,62,62); clear: both; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box !important; padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px; min-height: 1em; padding-left: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; font: 16px/1.75em 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62,62,62); clear: both; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">１９７８年文本规定授予品种权的作用，是在对受保护品种的有性或无性繁殖材料进行如下处理时，应事先征得育种者的同意：商业销售目的进行的生产、许可出售、市场销售。在保护领域内，两个文本均保护授权品种的繁殖材料，但对收获材料的保护上，７８文本规定成员国可以自由选择是否对收获材料进行保护。而１９９１年文本则做了明显的扩展。该文本规定<span style="box-sizing: border-box !important; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; background: yellow; padding-top: 0px">保护品种繁殖材料在生产或繁殖、为繁殖而进行的处理、许可出售、出售或其它市场销售、出口、进口以及出于上述目的的贮存需要育种者的授权。</span>在保护的领域上对收获的材料规定未经授权使用受保护品种的繁殖材料而获得的收获材料，包括整株和植株部分，应得到育种者授权，但育种者对繁殖材料已有合理机会行使其权利的情况除外。对直接从授权品种收获材料所获得的产品的保护规定各项活动，未经授权使用的受保护品种收获材料直接制作的产品，应得到育种者授权，但育种者对繁殖材料已有合理机会行使其权利的情况除外。而此在１９７８年的文本中是没有明确规定的，以上可以看出<span style="box-sizing: border-box !important; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; background: yellow; padding-top: 0px">１９９１年文本对授权品种保护的范围更广，力度更强，以上规定显著扩展了植物品种权的范畴，同时也大大加强了育种权利人的权利。</span></p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box !important; padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px; min-height: 1em; padding-left: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; font: 16px/1.75em 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62,62,62); clear: both; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box !important; padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px; min-height: 1em; padding-left: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; font: 16px/1.75em 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62,62,62); clear: both; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box !important; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; padding-top: 0px"><span style="box-sizing: border-box !important; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; background: yellow; padding-top: 0px">４．农民特权规定不同</span></strong></p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box !important; padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px; min-height: 1em; padding-left: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; font: 16px/1.75em 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62,62,62); clear: both; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box !important; padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px; min-height: 1em; padding-left: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; font: 16px/1.75em 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62,62,62); clear: both; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">从各国以及历史情况来看，对农民利用受保护品种在自己的土地上以种植为目的生产种子的行为，被排除在育种者权利保护范围之外，即所谓的&ldquo;农民特权&rdquo;。ＵＰＯＶ也维护了这个原则，但做法要求上有所变化。１９７８年文本规定：农民特权强制应用于所有植物属或种，除了为商业目的的生产外，其他生产活动是被允许的。而１９９１年文本则规定：<span style="box-sizing: border-box !important; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; background: yellow; padding-top: 0px">农民特权的应用在政府的控制之下。缔约方可以在合理的范围内，在保护育种者合法权益的条件下，对品种权进行限制。允许农民使用在自己土地上种植的保护品种的收获产品，在自己的土地上为繁殖的目的进行的生产活动。</span>这表明，ＵＰＯＶ成员国政府可以自行规定农民特权的有无或享有程度，条约不再对此有强制性要求，这实际上是为加强育种者权利提供了更大的空间。</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box !important; padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px; min-height: 1em; padding-left: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; font: 16px/26px 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62,62,62); clear: both; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box !important; padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px; min-height: 1em; padding-left: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; font: 16px/1.75em 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62,62,62); clear: both; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box !important; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; padding-top: 0px"><span style="box-sizing: border-box !important; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; background: yellow; padding-top: 0px">５．实质性派生品种商业开发时是否需品种权人授权不同</span></strong></p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box !important; padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px; min-height: 1em; padding-left: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; font: 16px/1.75em 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62,62,62); clear: both; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box !important; padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px; min-height: 1em; padding-left: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; font: 16px/1.75em 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62,62,62); clear: both; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px"><span style="box-sizing: border-box !important; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(0,176,80); padding-top: 0px">所谓实质性派生品种，是指从原始品种依赖型派生，同时又保留着原始品种的基本特征，但与原始品种有明显的区别，并且除派生引起的性状有所差异外，在基本特征的表达方面与原始品种一致，具有这些基本条件的品种称为实质性派生品种。</span>两个文本关于对待实质性派生品种也是有区别的：１９７８年文本规定实质性派生品种是应被保护的，也是能够商业开发的，<span style="box-sizing: border-box !important; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; background: yellow; padding-top: 0px">在１９９１年文本则规定实质性派生品种应被保护，但在商业开发上则需要原品种权拥有人的授权。</span></p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box !important; padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px; min-height: 1em; padding-left: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; font: 16px/1.75em 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62,62,62); clear: both; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px"><span style="box-sizing: border-box !important; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; background: yellow; padding-top: 0px"><img data-="" data-ratio="0.7193675889328063" data-s="300,640" data-type="png" data-w="" src="data:image/png;base64," style="box-sizing: border-box !important; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; width: 700px !important; padding-right: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; height: 503px !important; visibility: visible !important; padding-top: 0px" /></span></p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box !important; padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px; min-height: 1em; padding-left: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; font: 16px/1.75em 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62,62,62); clear: both; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box !important; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; padding-top: 0px"><span style="box-sizing: border-box !important; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; background: yellow; padding-top: 0px">６．品种权的保护期限不同</span></strong></p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box !important; padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px; min-height: 1em; padding-left: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; font: 16px/1.75em 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62,62,62); clear: both; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box !important; padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px; min-height: 1em; padding-left: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; font: 16px/1.75em 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62,62,62); clear: both; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">１９７８年文本规定：从授予品种权之日起，保护期限不少于１５年。藤本植物、林木、果树和观赏树木，包括其砧木，保护期不少于１８年。而１９９１年文本则规定：<span style="box-sizing: border-box !important; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; background: yellow; padding-top: 0px">该期限应自授予品种权之日起不少于２０年，</span>对于木本和藤本植物，该期限应自所述之日起不少于２５年，这一修改体现了对植物育种创造的进一步鼓励，也考虑到了育种技术的特性以及不同类型植物育种的特点，同时反映了植物品种专门保护制度与国际发明专利制度有关专利保护期限的协调。</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box !important; padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px; min-height: 1em; padding-left: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; font: 16px/1.75em 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62,62,62); clear: both; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box !important; padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px; min-height: 1em; padding-left: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; font: 16px/1.75em 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62,62,62); clear: both; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box !important; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; padding-top: 0px"><span style="box-sizing: border-box !important; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; background: yellow; padding-top: 0px">注：</span></strong>1.本文节选自廖秀健，谢　丹. ＵＰＯＶ９１文本与７８文本的区别及其对我国的影响，湖南科技大学学报（社会科学版）[J]第１３卷，第２期 ２０１０年３月</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box !important; padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px; min-height: 1em; padding-left: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; font: 16px/26px 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62,62,62); clear: both; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">2.图片均来自UPOV网站。</p>
